D E _ M U I N A I S S A U N A

By NakkiMaisteri

OBJECTIVE

 Terrorists: Plant the bomb in one out of three "sauna", area on the map and destroy the pyramid along with the religion. Counter terrorists: Protect the pyramid from demolition by all cost!

MAP INFORMATION

Map contains: "secret areas / Weapons / Three bomb sites" 
Recommented players/Max players: 24/34 
Spawnpoints: Terrorists spawn from the mountains. Counter terrorists spawn from the entrance of the pyramid. 
All of the map isn't in the screenshots, EXPLORE!

Download --> Test --> Comment --> Rate.
